lead_paragraph: A pro-Hillary Rodham Clinton super PAC is dispatching staffers to key states before the fall elections and helping Senate candidates with fundraising, laying the foundation for a potential Clinton presidential bid in 2016.

headline.main: Pro-Hillary Clinton Group Helping Senate Democrats
headline.print_headline: Pro-Hillary Clinton Group Helping Senate Democrats
